Reasoning: The paper deals with the statistical properties of co-channel interference (CCI) in downlink OFDMA systems and its impact on the spectral efficiency. This involves concepts from information theory (IT), networking and internet architecture (NI), communication (COMM), systems and control (SY), and multimedia (MM). Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.IT, followed by cs.NI, cs.COMM, cs.SY, and cs.MM.
